# Security Policies

---

## Mandatory Security Layers

## Authentication

- JWT authentication
- Refresh tokens
- Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)
- Password hashing using Argon2

---

## Authorization

- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
- Attribute-Based Access Control (ABAC) for advanced controls
- Dynamic database-driven menus

---

## Data Security

- AES encryption for sensitive fields
- TLS everywhere
- Secure object storage
- Secrets manager

---

## Compliance

- Consent logs
- Audit trails
- Access logs
- HIPAA / GDPR-aligned retention policies
- Backup + disaster recovery

---

## Monitoring

- SIEM integration
- Intrusion alerts
- Session anomaly detection
- API throttling